parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause injuries to the driver and passengers, and may lead to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags deploy without warning
airbags deploy in the absence of a crash or impact
airbags deploy while driving on the highway
airbags deploy during normal driving conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
airbags do not deploy despite the severity of the impact
seat belts do not restrain properly
occupants are thrown forward abruptly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt restraint system can lead to inadequate protection in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to occupants.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to restrain the occupant properly
the seat belt does not lock in place
the seat belt is loose or does not tighten properly
the seat belt is damaged or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the control arms and crossmember can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially during turns or braking.
symptoms: The vehicle's front end sways from left to right
the vehicle pulls in one direction
loss of control while driving
abnormal vehicle maneuvering.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Power Loss and Loud Noise
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of engine power and loud noise can cause the vehicle to stall or become difficult to control, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loud noise from the engine
loss of engine power
inability to exceed a certain speed (e.g.
20 mph)
vehicle stalls or becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission snap ring/wave spring can cause difficulty shifting gears, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents. Additionally, the broken metal pieces can clog the filter and damage the transmission, resulting in costly repairs.
symptoms: Difficulty shifting gears
feeling of gears getting stuck
jerking or jolting sensation when shifting
neutral light flashing
loss of power or acceleration
inability to pick up speed.
